@startuml
autonumber
actor User
participant "Camera" as Camera
participant "YOLOv5 Model" as YOLOv5Model
participant "Background Subtraction (BS)" as BackgroundSubtractionBS
participant "Histogram Equalization" as HistogramEqualization
participant "Threading" as Threading
participant "Multiprocessing" as Multiprocessing
participant "Gesture Recognition" as GestureRecognition
participant "Face Recognition" as FaceRecognition
participant "Hand Tracking" as HandTracking
participant "Single-Hand Interaction" as SingleHandInteraction
participant "Custom Gesture Actions" as CustomGestureActions
Camera ->> YOLOv5Model : Capture facial features
YOLOv5Model -> BackgroundSubtractionBS : Detect face
BackgroundSubtractionBS -> HistogramEqualization : Enhance image contrast
HistogramEqualization ->> GestureRecognition : Recognize hand gestures
Camera ->> GestureRecognition : Capture hand gesture commands
GestureRecognition -> HandTracking : Track hand movements
HandTracking -> SingleHandInteraction : Enable single-hand interaction
SingleHandInteraction -> CustomGestureActions : Customize gesture actions
Camera ->> FaceRecognition : Capture facial features
FaceRecognition -> SingleHandInteraction : Enable single-hand interaction
BackgroundSubtractionBS ->> Multiprocessing : Process background subtraction
Multiprocessing -> Threading : Enable concurrent execution
Threading -> CustomGestureActions : Customize gesture actions
@enduml